snippet.title: 3 out of 10: Season 2 - Announcement!
snippet.description: Season 2 of the unique playable sitcom, 3 out of 10, is coming to the Epic Game Store on April 8th, 2020! Experience all the chaos of game development at the world's worst game dev studio, as they try to finally make a game that scores better than "3 out of 10". Will this be the season that they finally do it?
